    "5663325": {
      "title": "V3D enables real-time 3D visualization and quantitative analysis of large-scale biological image data sets",
      "abstract": "High-throughput imaging generates massive data sets that are difficult to quantitatively analyze by hand. Peng et al. describe customizable software for visualizing and working with multi-gigabyte three-dimensional images in real time."
